            <ab>(Ö) On receiving this letter join us at Purrheia, and bring with you the man from Kerkesephis, exhorting him on my behalf. For you will confer Ö about the unsold Ö We shall release (you? it?) immediately. Good-bye. The 24th year, Thoth 15.</ab>
